7 Layer OSI

1) Physical
- Redundancy system
- Uninterruptible power supply

2) Data Link
- Managed switch

3) Network
- Address Resolution Protocol (ARP) (IP::MAC ADDR)
- Basic Firewall - Access Control List (ACL)(Router)
- External firewall device

4) Transport
- Advance firewall - Intrusion detection system (IDS)
- SSH key

5) Session
- Open socket session (socket(),connect(),listen(),accept(),send(),close())
- HTTP GET request standard (RFC2616)
- curl (have c lib) / wget (CLI)  
- Stateful inspection firewall

6) Presentation
- Encryption and data formatting

7) Application 
- Container - Docker
- Orchestration - kubenetes, ansible, terraform
- SSH key 

0) Others
- Protocol Data Unit (PDU) (Header for each layer)
- ACL/Firewall by opening or closing port
- ACL/Firewall by Packet filtering
- Packet capturing - tcpdump, wireshark
- Strong Password
